Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:21.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦の時代は、すでに何年もの長きに渡り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この国に続いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:30.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,血と慟哭の光景は、往時も何ひとつ変わりなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:46.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殺せ！早く…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:58.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだ生きて逆らう者どもに思い知らせよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:07.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんた！あんたー！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:12.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それも晒しとけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wars had ravaged the land for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The soil was soaked with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The wailings of the bloody survivors  \N could be heard throughout the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kill me, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let those who live to rebel \Ntake this as a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No dear, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang that up there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still wanna dance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, one day my passion's fire will
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One day the flames would die out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought I didn't need anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But even now, I'm so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... but I'm gonna burn it up, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling, it's not that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely it's not that bad either
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby. \NI'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up \NAh... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up \NAh... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby.  \N I'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,#3 The story of Jukai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing compared to \Nwhat he did for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to him, \Nmy son can run around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This world isn't such a bad place \Nwith a man like him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can move it \Nwith your shoulder muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All you'll need is a little practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy for you, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really letting me have this \Nfor free?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I do this because I wish to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach this man how to use his new limb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Jukai is like Buddha himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Master gave me a reason to live  \N when I was an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to be able to work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been up all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts, Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost at the doctor's place. \NHang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Dr. Jukai's home close by?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A passing samurai picked a fight with him \Nand cut his arm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My poor son...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Master will save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It may take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll do everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh doctor, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be running around again in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid the doctor might be \Na scary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm ever so glad I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You should never believe rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That you used to serve Lord Shiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A foreign ship picked me up \Nafter I'd fallen into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I went with them to their country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I learned how to make prosthetics \Nfor those who've lost their limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare not say it's to atone for my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But to just die peacefully \Nas if nothing happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think it could be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to have died, \Nbut was made to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It meant there was something \NI still had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,During the war with the Shiba clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,my father was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, Father...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You killed Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Begging for your life after what you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I care not for my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you wish \Nwhen this job is over. Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,let me fulfill my promise to that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You could never atone for what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never be my salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be... alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You wish to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"ONE YEAR LATER"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it born?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is a boy, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He will be my heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"6 YEARS LATER"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like that crab took a liking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, you'll scratch your mask up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take some home for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, I was made to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy is missing many body parts  \N and doesn't seem to hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But, he has a curious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The strong power to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"MARU"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"HYAKKIMARU"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things in this world \Nmore terrifying than a hundred demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't succumb to them, Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You will overcome them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be drawn to his powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't protect you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In order for you to survive on your own...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You win, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Tahomaru, how strong you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm the strongest in this land!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sword practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, put me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, tell me about your last war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I must dress his wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He feels no pain, \Ntherefore he knows no fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He has no hesitation \Ntowards slashing and killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wished for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For him to overcome his destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And live strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all, at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I made the wrong decision again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your right leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've been rough on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A leg. A real leg is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghouls don't just eat people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At times, they delude humans  \N and lend them their powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They let a person benefit  \N from their supernatural powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But in return, they take something away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be that your body was taken  \N from you in such an arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go with you. \NI'd only be in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All I did was teach you to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You had this with you when I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It may help you one day \Nto find your real parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So if he goes around killing monsters, \Nhe'll get his body back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I suppose that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody must've made a deal \Nwith the demons a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In return for that boy's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what they got, \Nbut his eyes, nose, mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,they gave it all away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One must be prepared to go to hell \Nto do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do these monsters want them for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A single eye couldn't \Nmake their tummies full.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? Maybe it fulfills their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've regained your sense of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you'll get burnt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorrow scatters in the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.11,0:22:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,piling up to form shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our footsteps admonish \Nindifference in such verbose ways
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As I peek into your fathomless eyes, \NI lose my composure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any hope \Nin the place I am heading to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I feign amusement and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.39,0:23:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because this road is so dark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be there to shine the light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to playing at saying goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but I cried when I waved to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fiery woes fade... and fade... \Nuntil night falls upon us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew tomorrow would be so mundane,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have said that I wanted to live
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's futile but can't help dreaming \Nof a future... a future... you are to blame
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:27.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おーい！カナメー！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:29.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こんにちはー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:32.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これ、先生に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:37.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんの！こんなんじゃお礼にもなんねぇけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:42.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,先生のおかげで、せがれはまた走れるようになったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:46.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんな人がいてくれるんだ。この世もまだ見捨てたもんじゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:57.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,肩の筋肉の力で曲がるようになっている。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,練習すれば必ず動かせる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:03.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉ…腕だ…！俺の…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんた！よかったね！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:09.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本当にいいんですかい？こんなすげぇものをタダで…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:12.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしの勝手でやってることだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありがとうごぜぇます！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,師匠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この男に使い方を教えてやってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:19.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,寿海先生は神様みてぇなお人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:26.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えぇ。本当に…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:40.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,師匠は、みなし子だった俺に生きる意味をくれた。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:44.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここで働ける俺は、幸せ者です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:10.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,師匠…今までずっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:27.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,痛いよぉ…おっ母…痛い…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:31.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう少しでお医者様のところだから、頑張っておくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:34.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,痛いよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:36.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしましたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,寿海先生の家は、この先でしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:47.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この子の腕を！通りがかりのお侍に言いがかりをつけられて…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:48.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こんな…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:54.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫です。師匠なら必ず助けてくれます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ふむ…少し時間がかかるかもしれんが、
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,できるだけのことはしてみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:12.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほんとですか！ありがとうございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:16.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よかった…よかったね…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:22.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本当に本当に、ありがとうございました！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:25.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すぐに元気に遊べるようになりますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:29.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,実は、どれだけ怖い人かと思ってましたけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,来てみて本当によかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人の噂なんて、当てにならないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,噂？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,い、いえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,カナメ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:54.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,師匠…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本当なんですか。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:05.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたが昔、斯波殿に仕えていた…というのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:21.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,海に落ちたわしを拾ったのは、大陸の船だった…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのまま大陸に渡ったわしは、
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:30.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手足を失った者たちに作りものの手足を補う技と出会った
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:34.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,罪滅ぼしなどと言うつもりはない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:39.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただ、何もせぬまま死んで楽になるのだけは…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,許されぬと思ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:49.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一度死んだはずのわしは生かされた。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしにはまだ、すべきことがあると…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:56.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,斯波領、金井氏の戦で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:59.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私の父も死にました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:02.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上…父上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:13.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前が…お前が父上を！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:15.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,カナメ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,た…頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,命乞いか、今さら！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:26.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしの命などいくらでもやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:29.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この仕事が済んだら、いかようにしても構わん。だが、
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの親子との約束だけは…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの子のためだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すまぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありがとう！先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さようならー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:32.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,償えるはずがない…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:40.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたは…俺を救えない！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:50.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生きているのか！こんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:56.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生きたい…のか…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:08.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生まれたか！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:12.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい、男の子にございます
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっほほぉーっ！でかしたぞ奥！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:18.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,立派な跡継ぎじゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前その蟹にたいそう好かれたようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,無理をするとその面に傷がつくぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何匹か持って帰って焼いてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そろそろ戻ろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしは再び生かされた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:28.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,身体のあちこちを欠き、\Nこちらの言うこともどこまで伝わっているのかもわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:38.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが、この子には…不思議な力がある
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:47.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生き抜くための、強い力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:57.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前の名前だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:06.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この世には何百の鬼よりも恐ろしいものがいくらでもある。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが負けるな。百鬼丸。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが負けるな。百鬼丸。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:57.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸！大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今のは一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:14.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん？どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:23.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,物の怪が！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:32.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この子の力に惹かれ集まってくるのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:37.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:42.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしも、いつまでもお前を守ってやれるわけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:45.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前が1人で生きていくために…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,強くなるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:01.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉ…参りました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:04.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さすが多宝丸さま！お強い！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:09.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうだ！僕はこの国で一番強いんだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:10.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,剣の稽古か
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:14.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,高い！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:20.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっ、母上ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:29.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:36.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それより父上、このあいだの戦の話をお聞かせください！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハハ、よかろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:43.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手当をしてやらねば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:57.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,痛みを知らねば、恐れも感じぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:03.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,切り刻み、殺し、命を奪うことになんの躊躇いも生じはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:14.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お願いはただ一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:21.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生まれ持った運命に負けず、
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,強く生きてほしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:27.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただそれだけのはずだっ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:36.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしはまた！間違ったのか…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸！無事か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:19.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,右足が…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手荒く動かしたからか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こ、これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一体何が！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な、なんということだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:41.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,脚だ！生身の脚が生えた！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:43.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしてこのようなことが…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:06.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやかしとは、人を食らうだけのものではない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:12.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ときに彼らは人の心を惑わし、その力を貸し与えもする
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:17.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人智を超えた力で以て人に恩恵を与え
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:22.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,代償として、人から何かを奪ってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:29.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前もそういう因果の中で、\N奴らに身体を奪われたのやもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:36.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしは行けん。足手まといになるばかりだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:41.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,結局、何もしてやれなかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:47.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしはただ殺生を教えただけで…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:52.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前を拾ったとき身につけていたお守りだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:57.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,持っていけば、どこかで本当の親と会えるやもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:47.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,つまり、化け物をぶっ殺して回ると取られた\N身体が戻ってくるってわけか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:51.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そういうことなんだろうねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:56.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,昔、誰かが化け物どもと取引でもしたんだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの子の身体と引き換えにね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひでぇじゃねぇか！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:04.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何貰ったんだか知らねぇけど、目も鼻も口も、
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:06.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,丸ごとぜーんぶやっちまうなんてよぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:11.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ、地獄に堕ちる覚悟でもなきゃできないことさね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:15.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ！なんでバケモンどもはそんなん欲しがるんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:19.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,目ン玉ひとつ食ったって腹の足しにはなんねぇだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:23.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さてね。心の足しにはなるのかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだよそりゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん？百鬼丸！起きたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:30.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お、おい…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へっ、熱かったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:38.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なるほど、痛みが戻ったか
